# Lesson 2 – Manager Tools: Power Triangle & The Trinity

**Course:** Leadership & Management Class Program (1 hour / week)  
**Date:** TBD  
**Duration:** 60 minutes  
**Prerequisite lesson:** Lesson 1 – Manager Tools: Three Pillars of Leadership

## Learning Objectives

By the end of this session, participants will be able to:

- Summarize the Three Pillars of Leadership and connect them to their own team.
- Explain the three types of power in the Power Triangle.
- Distinguish how junior and senior leaders typically rely on different types of power.
- Describe how the Manager Tools Trinity (1on1s, Feedback, Coaching, Delegation) supports the Three Pillars.
- Identify one concrete experiment with 1on1s to shift from relying on position power to relationship and inspirational power.

